---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import BookingModal from '../components/BookingModal.jsx';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Beranda"
  description="DFreeze Vet Clinic – Klinik hewan terpercaya untuk perawatan kesehatan hewan peliharaan Anda. Konsultasi, vaksinasi, grooming, dan bedah."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-20 md:py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background decoration -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[500px] bg-blue-50 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-60"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-sky-100 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-40"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-blue-200">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500 animate-pulse"></span>
          Dokter Hewan Berpengalaman 24/7
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight tracking-tight">
          Kesehatan Optimal untuk
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-blue-600 to-sky-500">
            Hewan Peliharaan
          </span>
          Anda
        </h1>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-500 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
          DFreeze Vet Clinic hadir dengan tim dokter hewan profesional, peralatan medis modern, dan pelayanan penuh kasih untuk memastikan sahabat berbulu Anda selalu sehat dan bahagia.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 items-center">
          <BookingModal client:load />
          <a
            href="/artikel"
            id="cta-artikel"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-700 font-semibold hover:text-blue-800 hover:gap-3 transition-all"
          >
            Baca Artikel Kesehatan
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-8 pt-4 border-t border-slate-100">
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">5000+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-0.5">Pasien Ditangani</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">10+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-0.5">Tahun Pengalaman</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">4.9⭐</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-0.5">Rating Kepuasan</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Hero Illustration -->
      <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
        <div class="relative w-full max-w-lg">
          <div class="w-full aspect-square bg-linear-to-br from-blue-100 via-sky-50 to-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl flex items-center justify-center p-8">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 200 200" class="w-full h-full max-w-xs">
              <!-- Vet cross background -->
              <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="90" fill="#EFF6FF" stroke="#BFDBFE" stroke-width="2"/>
              <!-- Dog body -->
              <ellipse cx="100" cy="120" rx="38" ry="30" fill="#FDE68A"/>
              <!-- Dog head -->
              <circle cx="100" cy="85" r="25" fill="#FDE68A"/>
              <!-- Dog ears -->
              <ellipse cx="80" cy="68" rx="12" ry="16" fill="#F59E0B" transform="rotate(-15 80 68)"/>
              <ellipse cx="120" cy="68" rx="12" ry="16" fill="#F59E0B" transform="rotate(15 120 68)"/>
              <!-- Dog eyes -->
              <circle cx="92" cy="82" r="4" fill="#1E3A5F"/>
              <circle cx="108" cy="82" r="4" fill="#1E3A5F"/>
              <circle cx="93.5" cy="80.5" r="1.5" fill="white"/>
              <circle cx="109.5" cy="80.5" r="1.5" fill="white"/>
              <!-- Dog nose -->
              <ellipse cx="100" cy="91" rx="5" ry="3.5" fill="#B45309"/>
              <!-- Dog mouth -->
              <path d="M95 95 Q100 100 105 95" fill="none" stroke="#B45309" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <!-- Dog paws -->
              <ellipse cx="72" cy="148" rx="12" ry="9" fill="#FDE68A"/>
              <ellipse cx="128" cy="148" rx="12" ry="9" fill="#FDE68A"/>
              <!-- Stethoscope -->
              <path d="M110 105 Q130 105 130 120 Q130 135 115 135" fill="none" stroke="#2563EB" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <circle cx="115" cy="138" r="6" fill="#2563EB"/>
              <circle cx="115" cy="138" r="3" fill="#DBEAFE"/>
              <circle cx="110" cy="105" r="4" fill="#2563EB"/>
              <!-- Medical cross -->
              <rect x="155" y="30" width="25" height="8" rx="3" fill="#2563EB"/>
              <rect x="162" y="23" width="8" height="22" rx="3" fill="#2563EB"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <!-- Floating cards -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg px-4 py-3 flex items-center gap-2 border border-slate-100">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 text-base">✓</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-800">Vaksinasi Lengkap</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Semua jenis hewan</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg px-4 py-3 flex items-center gap-2 border border-slate-100">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 text-base">🏥</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-800">Rawat Inap 24 Jam</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Pantauan intensif</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Layanan Section -->
  <section id="layanan" class="py-20 border-t border-slate-100">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <span class="text-blue-600 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest">Layanan Kami</span>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Perawatan Lengkap untuk Hewan Peliharaan</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Kami menyediakan berbagai layanan medis veteriner berkualitas tinggi dengan teknologi terkini dan penanganan penuh kasih sayang.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Service 1 -->
      <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-7 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-13 h-13 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-blue-100 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Konsultasi Umum</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Pemeriksaan kesehatan menyeluruh oleh dokter hewan berpengalaman untuk diagnosis akurat dan perawatan optimal.</p>
        <div class="mt-5 text-blue-600 text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:gap-2 transition-all">
          Pelajari lebih lanjut
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 2 -->
      <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-7 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-sky-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-sky-100 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M9 12h6"/><path d="M12 9v6"/>
            <path d="M3.6 9h16.8a.6.6 0 0 1 .6.6v6.8a.6.6 0 0 1-.6.6H3.6a.6.6 0 0 1-.6-.6V9.6a.6.6 0 0 1 .6-.6Z"/>
            <path d="M8 9V7a4 4 0 0 1 8 0v2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Vaksinasi</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Program vaksinasi lengkap dan terjadwal untuk melindungi hewan peliharaan dari berbagai penyakit berbahaya.</p>
        <div class="mt-5 text-blue-600 text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:gap-2 transition-all">
          Pelajari lebih lanjut
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 3 -->
      <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-7 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-violet-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-violet-100 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#7c3aed" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M3 22a1 1 0 0 1-1-1v-5a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h2a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v5a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H3Z"/>
            <path d="M10 22a1 1 0 0 1-1-1v-5a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h2a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v5a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-2Z"/>
            <path d="M14 13h-4v-3c0-2.2 1.8-4 4-4V3h2v3a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v3h-4v1.5a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H15a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V13Z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Grooming</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Layanan perawatan kebersihan dan penampilan hewan peliharaan Anda oleh groomer profesional berstandar internasional.</p>
        <div class="mt-5 text-blue-600 text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:gap-2 transition-all">
          Pelajari lebih lanjut
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 4 -->
      <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-7 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-green-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-green-100 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Laboratorium & Diagnostik</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Fasilitas lab modern untuk pemeriksaan darah, urin, dan diagnostik imaging (X-Ray, USG) dengan hasil cepat dan akurat.</p>
        <div class="mt-5 text-blue-600 text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:gap-2 transition-all">
          Pelajari lebih lanjut
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 5 -->
      <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-7 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-amber-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-amber-100 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#d97706" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 22a10 10 0 1 0 0-20 10 10 0 0 0 0 20Z"/>
            <path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Rawat Inap</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Fasilitas rawat inap 24 jam dengan pemantauan ketat oleh tim medis berdedikasi untuk pemulihan yang optimal.</p>
        <div class="mt-5 text-blue-600 text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:gap-2 transition-all">
          Pelajari lebih lanjut
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 6 -->
      <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-7 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-red-100 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Bedah & Sterilisasi</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Prosedur bedah dengan standar higienitas tinggi, mulai dari sterilisasi, pengangkatan tumor, hingga ortopedi.</p>
        <div class="mt-5 text-blue-600 text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:gap-2 transition-all">
          Pelajari lebih lanjut
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Us Section -->
  <section class="py-20 border-t border-slate-100">
    <div class="bg-linear-to-br from-blue-600 via-blue-700 to-sky-700 rounded-3xl p-10 md:p-16 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Background decoration -->
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-80 h-80 bg-white/5 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-60 h-60 bg-white/5 rounded-full translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2"></div>

      <div class="relative grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <span class="text-blue-200 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest">Mengapa Memilih Kami?</span>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
            Kepercayaan Ribuan Pemilik Hewan Peliharaan
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-blue-100 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            Sejak 2014, kami telah melayani kebutuhan medis hewan peliharaan dengan standar tertinggi dan penuh empati. Kepercayaan Anda adalah prioritas utama kami.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8">
            <BookingModal client:load />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-5 border border-white/20">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🏥</div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Fasilitas Modern</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-100 mt-1">Peralatan medis berteknologi tinggi dan ruang operasi steril berstandar internasional.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-5 border border-white/20">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">👨‍⚕️</div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Dokter Berpengalaman</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-100 mt-1">Tim dokter hewan bersertifikasi dengan pengalaman lebih dari 10 tahun di bidangnya.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-5 border border-white/20">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">⏰</div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Layanan 24 Jam</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-100 mt-1">Siap melayani darurat kapan saja, termasuk malam hari, akhir pekan, dan hari libur.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-5 border border-white/20">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">💊</div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Obat Berkualitas</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-100 mt-1">Penggunaan obat-obatan berlisensi dan produk perawatan yang aman untuk hewan peliharaan.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
